messages.message:
AWS will end support for EKS AL2-optimized and AL2-accelerated AMIs, effective November 26, 2025. If you are deploying EKS clusters to host an application, please plan to migrate to AL2023 or Bottlerocket AMIs by Q3 2025.
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/eks/latest/userguide/eks-ami-deprecation-faqs.html
cc @Ashish
